                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>that part of the ceiling of the synagogue gave way some time<lb/>\n                                        ago &amp; we have taken the opportunity which obliged to\n                                        repair<lb/> to have the whole building cleaned &amp; the\n                                        walls painted<lb/> which has much improved the appearance of\n                                        our pretty<lb/> little place of worship. I have to thank you\n                                        for the<lb/> proof you sent me of the presentation to\n                                                  <persName>Desola</persName> and<lb/>\n                                        <add>?</add> to congratulate you on the receipt of a similar\n                                        present</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">In further news Refer you to our friend\n                                                  <persName>Graff<add>?</add></persName></p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(7)\">I <add>?</add> truly yours</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(8)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">\n                                                  <add>?</add>\n                                        </persName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(7)\">\n                                        <placeName>Montreal</placeName>\n                                        <date>20 March '51</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <div>\n                                        <p>\n                                                  <ref target=\"Occident_PDFs/Occ_9_2.pdf\">The above\n                                                  text refers to Occident Volume 9 No. 2 pages 120\n                                                  through 121. Click here to view.</ref>\n                                        </p>\n                              </div>\n                    </body>\n          </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
